<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><id>https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=57&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0</id><title>HKDiscuss money</title><updated>2025-05-18T10:38:45.506374+00:00</updated><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=57&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0"/><generator uri="https://lkiesow.github.io/python-feedgen" version="1.0.0">python-feedgen</generator><subtitle>Latest articles</subtitle><entry><id>e0989cedc0872beb5e0276c6dbf6b996</id><title>8月左右將有特大消息,各位要把握時間部處!</title><updated>2025-05-18T12:59:48+08:00</updated><author><name>助紂為虐.臭萬年</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-18T12:59:48+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572455860"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572455860"&gt;到時將有一超級重量消息發佈,股市馬上大上大落,1天內1-2千點飛上飛落,到定下來之來,之後數天,港女會暴升,直逼3幻點,各位記得把握住,不要隨便在中途下錯車,要食大茶飯!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;但,股票雖然大升,小粉紅卻好失落,原本自己一直都是錯了&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="9" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/titter.gif"/&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31930908&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=10718173106829b8b5b58a15_68193549"/><published>2025-05-18T12:59:48+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>c8ddb0963ef374b4e0161874607babad</id><title>在1984年這時在元朗買層細樓都只係十幾廿萬附近</title><updated>2025-05-18T13:16:00+08:00</updated><author><name>edwin8888</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-18T13:16:00+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572456090"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572456090"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16233454" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="p